ktuelle Fotos, neue Übersetzungen der Briefe des Fürsten Orsini und bietet neue Erkenntnisse durch Zugang zu allen Regionen des Heiligen Waldes.  aIn his famous garden that "resembles only itself and no others," Vicino Orsini takes the visitor on the journey of a lifetime, divulging adventures, secrets, and beautiful goddesses in magical and strange places. New insights are provided by previously unpublished material – including artworks, photos, and new translations of the prince’s letters – and rarely granted access to all parts of the sacred grove.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 0aGardensxItalyxBomarzo. 0aGardenszItalyzBomarzo. 0aSculpture, EtruscanxItalyxBomarzo. 0aSculpture, EtruscanzItalyzBomarzo. 0aSculpture, RenaissancexItalyxBomarzo. 0aSculpture, RenaissancezItalyzBomarzo. 4aBomarzo. 4aLandschaftsdesign. 7aARCHITECTURE / Landscape.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2017 Part 1z978311076249508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2017z978311071954308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Architecture and Design 2017z9783110547719oZDB-23-DAD08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2017z9783110540550oZDB-23-DGG0 cprintz978303561203540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978303561053640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783035610536423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783035610536/original  a978-3-11-071954-3  DG Plus eBook-Package 2017b2017  a978-3-11-076249-5  DG Plus DeG Package 2017 Part 1b2017  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_AD  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DADb2017  aZDB-23-DGGb2017